<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/PhD-Fellowship-for-a-national-of-Benin-Food-Security-and-Nutrition" title="PhD Fellowship for a national of Benin: Food Security and Nutrition" alt="link">PhD Fellowship for a national of Benin: Food Security and Nutrition</a></h2>

	
					<p><b>Deadline: 24 April 2012.</b>Bioversity International and the Faculty of Agricultural Sciences of University of Abomey-Calavi (UAC) in Benin, in collaboration with Helsinki University, Finland, are recruiting a talented scientist for a partial sponsored PhD fellowship on food security and nutrition. The research will be conducted, in the framework of the project “Enhancing Food and Nutrition Security of Vulnerable Groups in Communities in Benin through Increased use of local Agricultural Biodiversity”, supported by the Government of Finland.<a href="http://www.bioversityinternational.org/training/other_fellowships_and_scholarships/phd_fellowship_for_a_national_of_benin_food_security_and_nutrition.html" target="_blank">http://www.bioversityinternational.org/training/other_fellowships_and_scholarships/phd_fellowship_for_a_national_of_benin_food_security_and_nutrition.html</a></p>
