					<p><b>Deadline: 1 June 2012</b>ONLINE EDUCA BERLIN offers a series of sessions over three days, ranging from formal presentations to informal and interactive workshops and seminars. Key topics relevant to the theme of ‘Reaching Beyond Tomorrow’ will be considered and research-based evidence presented. New learning environments, cutting edge technology and policy developments will also be highlighted.Visit the website for details: <a href="http://www.online-educa.com/call-for-papers" target="_self">http://www.online-educa.com/call-for-papers</a> </p>
