						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/The-African-Climate-Change-Fellowship-Programme-ACCFP-Call-for-applications-for-ACCFP-adaptation-teaching-fellowships" title="The African Climate Change Fellowship Programme (ACCFP): Call for applications for ACCFP adaptation teaching fellowships" alt="link">The African Climate Change Fellowship Programme (ACCFP): Call for applications for ACCFP adaptation teaching fellowships</a></h2>

	
					<p><b>Deadline: 12 March 2012</b>The Institute of Resource Assessment at the University of Dar Es Salaam (IRA-UDSM), in partnership with START and CCAA, announces the Call for Applications 2012 for the African Climate Change Fellowship Program (ACCFP). This Call solicits applications for Adaptation Teaching Fellowships. University educators who are citizens of an African nation and based at an African institution are eligible to apply. Applications are particularly encouraged from women and traditionally under-represented regions and countries in Africa. The ACCFP will support clearly defined activities that advance teaching, curriculum development and/or educational outreach in Climate Change Adaptation. The ACCFP offers experiential learning, education, and training opportunities to African educators and graduate students to enhance their capabilities for advancing and applying knowledge for climate change adaptation in Africa. Adaptation Teaching Fellows are expected to be innovative in their proposed work and ensure that this work reaches out to students as well as fellow educators. Adaptation Teaching Fellows do not conduct research activities. Priority will be given to design and development of interdisciplinary experiences and those that fit logically within and add value to existing programs.Visit the website for details: <a href="http://www.accfp.org/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=193&amp;Itemid=136" target="_self">http://www.accfp.org/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=193&amp;Itemid=136</a> </p>
							<p><span class="date">9/03/2012</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/The-African-Climate-Change-Fellowship-Programme-ACCFP-Call-for-applications-for-ACCFP-adaptation-teaching-fellowships">Read more...</a>
