<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/Request-for-Proposals-for-Evaluation-Services-in-relation-to-the-Canadian-International-Food-Security-Research-Fund-CIFSRF-Mid-Term-Evaluation" title="Request for Proposals for Evaluation Services in relation to the Canadian International Food Security Research Fund (CIFSRF) Mid-Term Evaluation " alt="link">Request for Proposals for Evaluation Services in relation to the Canadian International Food Security Research Fund (CIFSRF) Mid-Term Evaluation </a></h2>

	
					<p><b>Deadline for Submission: 15 March 2012</b>Download the details here: <a href="http://www.idrc.ca/EN/Funding/Competitions/Documents/RFP%20CIFSRF.pdf" target="_self">http://www.idrc.ca/EN/Funding/Competitions/Documents/RFP%20CIFSRF.pdf</a>The Canadian International Food Security Research Fund (CIFSRF), is issuing a call for proposals for a mid-term evaluative study of the Fund. CIFSRF is a five-year, CA$62million program, jointly funded by the International Development Research Centre and the Canadian International Development Agency (CIDA). The purpose of the mid-term evaluation is to provide an early progress report on program outcomes and achievement of objectives. The evaluation will also examine how CIFSRF operates and identify ways to improve performance. It will also provide strategic analysis to inform CIFSRF's second phase.Visit the website for details: <a href="http://www.idrc.ca/EN/Funding/Competitions/Pages/CompetitionDetails.aspx?CompetitionID=29" target="_self">http://www.idrc.ca/EN/Funding/Competitions/Pages/CompetitionDetails.aspx?CompetitionID=29</a></p>
							<p><span class="date">9/03/2012</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/Request-for-Proposals-for-Evaluation-Services-in-relation-to-the-Canadian-International-Food-Security-Research-Fund-CIFSRF-Mid-Term-Evaluation">Read more...</a>
</div>
